ygData.title: Transsexual People's List for the UK
ygData.description:
WELCOME TO TRANSSEXUAL UK
Advice, Information and Support within a safe environment

A fast growing group with a variety of discussion, Transsexual UK is a light hearted group with like minded members who share ideas and information, support one another, debate issues and often use the group as a social outlet. Whilst you are free to lurk, members are encouraged to ask questions and seek advice from the group, use the information resources, or simply just to enjoy a little social banter and a giggle.

THE BENEFITS OF MEMBERSHIP It's FREE A Safe and Friendly Environment Advice and Support Discussion Forum Electronic booklets Medical information News Web Site Links .. and much more! MEMBERSHIP IS OPEN TO Those questioning their gender identity Transsexual people, in role or not, pre or post-op Friends, Partners and Family members Professionals and Students

HOW TO JOIN

Send an e-mail to transsexual-uk-subscribe@yahoogroups.com. Carefully follow the instructions sent, we will process your request within 24hrs.

All members must be 16 years of age or over. Under 16's please contact Mermaids, a support group for children and teenagers.

WE LOOK FORWARD TO WELCOMING YOU SOON
